data.description: Don’t miss the chance to own this beautiful former model home w/stunning panoramic views in coveted Emerald Pointe. This Exquisite home welcomes you in w/ a cozy covered front porch & opens to a bright & sensible floorplan. Features complete solar system to offset your utility costs! Study w/ built in book cases off the foyer leading to an stunning open family room, kitchen & sunroom. Spacious kitchen w/white cabinets, granite counters & opens to a LG family room & sun/dining room w/soaring views, fireplace & shed. Upper level features 4 spacious bedrooms, including a primary w/en suite bath & valley views. Large back yard w/tons of space for entertaining. Electric Car Charging. Community offers parks, trails, athletic courts and clubhouse.
